@startuml
title Viaverse Admin / Moderation Action — Activity Diagram
start
:Admin action request;
:Admin MFA + session check;
:Check RBAC/ABAC\nresource scope;
if (Allowed?) then (yes)
  :Open case/resource;
  :Review evidence\nminimum necessary data;
  :Choose action;
  :Enter reason + notes;
  :Validate action policy\nseverity / cooldown / limits;
  :Apply domain action;
  :Write immutable audit log;
  :Notify affected user\nif policy allows;
  :Create appeal path\nif eligible;
  :Emit AdminActionApplied;
else (no)
  :Deny + audit attempt;
endif
stop

note bottom
Admin screens should reveal the minimum necessary data for the case.
Private messages/media require explicit reason and scoped access.
end note
@enduml
